hostname clab-spine-leaf-topology-n9kv-leaf

banner motd ^
Authorized access only. All activity may be monitored and reported.
^

feature tacacs+
tacacs-server host 10.0.0.1 key your_tacacs_secret
aaa group server tacacs+ TACACS
    server 10.0.0.1

aaa authentication login default group TACACS local
aaa authorization commands default group TACACS local
aaa accounting default group TACACS

no feature telnet
feature ssh
ssh key rsa 2048 force

ip domain-name example.com

username admin password 5 admin role network-admin

ntp server 192.168.1.1 use-vrf management
ntp server 192.168.1.2 use-vrf management

system default switchport
no ip igmp snooping

feature lldp

logging server 10.0.0.2 5 use-vrf management
logging server 10.0.0.3 5 use-vrf management
logging timestamp milliseconds
logging console 5

